# Stage 8: Perfect Shared Ending

label stage8_ending_shared_perfect:
    scene bg club_fair with fade

    show h at left
    show m at center
    show y at right
    with dissolve

    h "Can you believe it's been a week already?"
    m "Feels like both yesterday and a lifetime ago."
    y "I still can't quite remember where I put my old laptop. Gone, somehow."

    show l at left
    show k at right
    with dissolve

    l "Small prices. We all lost something trivial."
    k "But we gained understanding. Connection. Purpose."

    "Together, you shared the burden."
    "No one person lost too much."
    "And the Echo found peace."

    mc "We did it. All of us."

    "The academy thrives. Your friendships deeper than ever."
    "And sometimes, when the light hits the garden just right..."
    "You think you hear a whisper: 'Thank you.'"

    $ ending_type = "perfect_ending"

    jump stage8_epilogue_team
